<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>662</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men qí dǎo zài jīn tiān de qīng chén, wǒ men qí dǎo zài jīn tiān de lí míng qián.
 wǒ men qí dǎo huàn xǐng shuì zhe de rén, yī tóng qí dǎo hé píng.
 yuàn wǒ men de xīn yuàn huà zuò hé píng gē, fēi biàn tiān yá.
 yuàn wǒ men de xīn yuàn huà zuò hé píng gē, dài qù lǜ sè de gǎn lǎn.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men qí dǎo 迦南662</title>
</song>